                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-869061850" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-869061850" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="869061850">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/redhousepainter/">redhousepainter</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-03-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有几篇好像很多年前在杂志上看过，整体上没有尽头精彩，写契科夫那篇说到创新，说得非常透彻，可以平移至音乐圈。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="871741369">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-871741369" class="vote-count">26</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-871741369" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="871741369">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/d_andrew/">淡島百景</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">封面的咖啡印嚇我一跳...</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1079339389">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1079339389" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1079339389" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1079339389">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weitianze/">违天择</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-08-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">如果说这本书存在一个笼统的主题，应当是从非典型作品入手去理解作家，理想国加“重读”二字莫名其妙；唐诺难以收束的形式用来写《尽头》、《世间的名字》比较合适，写《在咖啡馆遇见14个作家》这样的书，频繁失焦有些尴尬。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

